(97, 'Madison-Keys-beats-Petra-Kvitova-in-Olympic-rematch-at-China-Open', 'Madison Keys beats Petra Kvitova in Olympic rematch at China Open', 'It took two hours and 40 minutes, three sets and two tiebreaks for Keys to end the challenge of the double Wimbledon champion, 6-3, 6-7 (2/7), 7-6 (7/5). A double fault by Kvitova turned the first set in favour of Keys, but she pulled back in the second, pushing it to a tiebreak, which she won. There was little between the pair in the final set, but Kvitova''s 32 unforced errors to Keys'' 25 ultimately cost the Czech a semi-final place -- and ended her eight-match winning streak.', '7 Oct 2016, 12:45 pm', NULL, 'http://news.yahoo.com/madison-keys-beats-petra-kvitova-olympic-rematch-china-104503443--ten.html', '2016-10-07 00:00:00', NULL, 'src="http://l3.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/_j35FnzKFQEJCJgBl34gTg--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztmaT1maWxsO2g9ODY7cT03NTt3PTEzMA--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/afp.com/3257dd1581f9d904b497957a9918016f3c9f07d4.jpg"', 'sports', NULL),
